name: Portrait of Bobi the Cat #02
description:
Since the first time he stroll around our apartment room during his stray time, he quick to get along with us. And not like other male domestic cat, he never spray his pee around to mark his territory. And that's just one of many things that makes me and wife felt over him and start to take care of him daily since then. 

This token is a series of portrait that taken during the second year he lived with us. Basking in the golden hour sun from our little studio apartment in the southern Jakarta capital, Indonesia.
